   If part: (!x. x IN s ==> f x IN t) ==> (IMAGE f s) SUBSET t
       y IN (IMAGE f s)
   ==> ?x. (y = f x) /\ x IN s   by IN_IMAGE
   ==> f x = y IN t              by given
   hence (IMAGE f s) SUBSET t    by SUBSET_DEF
   Only-if part: (IMAGE f s) SUBSET t ==>  (!x. x IN s ==> f x IN t)
