(* Proof:
   Let k = m DIV n.
   Since m <> 0, n divides m ==> n <> 0       by ZERO_DIVIDES
    Thus m = k * n                            by DIVIDES_EQN, 0 < n
      so 0 < k                                by MULT, NOT_ZERO_LT_ZERO
