   If a = 0,
      lcm 0 b = 0 = lcm 0 c          by LCM_0
   If a <> 0,
      If b = 0, a * b = 0 = c * a    by MULT_0, SUB_0
      Hence c = 0, hence true        by MULT_EQ_0
